The Uncle Henry Staglon Handle 3-Piece Fixed/Linerlock/Folder Combo offers a versatile set of knives designed to handle a wide range of cutting tasks from outdoor adventures to everyday use. The folder is built with a sturdy linerlock mechanism for secure blade use and features the same Staglon handle with stainless steel bolsters and inlaid shield tying the set together with a unified design
